Package: bibou
Type: Package
Title: Package bibou aims at formatting and using bibliographic data in a tidy way to help produce statistical and graphical analyses of a bibliometric corpus.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lise Vaudor
Maintainer: Lise Vaudor <lise.vaudor@ens-lyon.fr>
Description: The bibou package can be used to format bibliographic exports from web of science. It helps formatting these exports into tables, either with
    - one row per document (tib_doc), one row per document*author (tib_doc_author),
    - one row per document*keyword (tib_doc_keyword) or
    - one row per document*word of abstract (tib_doc_word).    
    It builds on packages bibliometrix, tidytext, and mixr.
